				<p>
					(914) 533-0333<br>
					700 Oakridge Common<br>
					South Salem, NY 10590<br>
					<a href="mailto:madetoshare@divvies.com">madetoshare@divvies.com</a>
				</p>
			</div>
			<hr class="thin fs-cell fs-lg-hide fs-md-hide fs-sm-3">
			<div class="fs-cell fs-lg-4 fs-md-2 fs-sm-3 text-center">
				<h2>Press or Media</h2>
